### Test Data Variables
@testBeerID = 999
@testBrewery = Test Brewery
@testCountry = Chile
@testPrice = 1500
@testCurrency = CLP

###

### Quick Health Check
# @name quickHealthCheck
GET {{baseURL}}/ping HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Create Test Beer with Variables
# @name createTestBeer
POST {{apiURL}}/beers HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": {{testBeerID}},
  "name": "Test Beer {{testBeerID}}",
  "brewery": "{{testBrewery}}",
  "country": "{{testCountry}}",
  "price": {{testPrice}},
  "currency": "{{testCurrency}}"
}

###

### Get Test Beer
# @name getTestBeer
GET {{apiURL}}/beers/{{testBeerID}} HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Calculate Box Price for Test Beer
# @name calculateTestBeerBoxPrice
GET {{apiURL}}/beers/{{testBeerID}}/boxprice?quantity=6&currency=USD HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{contentType}}

